data.description: Discover your dream home in the heart of Hampton: a beautifully maintained brick front ranch situated on 1+ acre. Nestled on a sprawling, level lot, this property boasts an ideal location and an array of features that cater to comfort, convenience, and lifestyle. Step inside to find a spacious family room, illuminated by natural light pouring through large windows, complemented by soaring vaulted ceilings that create an airy, open feel. The heart of this home is its expansive kitchen, designed for both cooking and socializing, making it perfect for gatherings. Adjacent to the kitchen, a versatile, sunlit flex space offers endless possibilities—transform it into your home office, a cozy sunroom, or an extra family room. Practicality is key in the thoughtful layout, with a laundry room equipped with storage cabinets situated conveniently among the bedrooms. Two sizeable secondary bedrooms boast large walk-in closets, providing ample storage. The impressive primary suite, stretching across the home's width, features a luxuriously designed bathroom complete with double vanities, a corner soaking tub, a separate shower, and an additional closet. Embrace the serene ambiance of this tranquil community from your front porch or the privacy of your fenced backyard patio. The property also features a 25X30 detached garage, a versatile space ideal for a workshop, hobby area, or extra storage. Location is paramount, and this home delivers, with all three schools within a half-mile radius, the excitement of the Atlanta Motor Speedway a mere 10-minute drive away, and the creativity hub of Trilith Studios in Fayetteville only 30 minutes away. Plus, with easy access to highways and a half-hour commute to Atlanta Hartsfield Jackson Airport, convenience is at your doorstep. The absence of an HOA enhances the property’s appeal, offering flexibility for those considering it as an investment for short or long-term rentals. This ranch home is a standout offering in Turner Creek, promising a blend of lifestyle, comfort, and convenience. Don’t miss out on this exceptional opportunity.
